longBusinessSummary: Atlas Cycles (Haryana) Limited manufactures and sells bicycles in India. Atlas Cycles (Haryana) Limited was formerly known as Atlas Cycle Industries Ltd and changed its name to Atlas Cycles (Haryana) Limited in April 2002. The company was incorporated in 1950 and is based in Sonepat, India.
